title: Koreans
summary: Koreans (South Korean: 한민족/한국인/한국사람, 韓民族/韓國人/韓國사람, Hanminjok/Hanguk-in/Hanguksaram, North Korean: 조선민족/조선인/조선사람, 朝鮮民族/朝鮮人/朝鮮사람, Joseonminjok/Joseonin/Joseonsaram, lit. 'Korean race'; see names of Korea) are an East Asian ethnic group native to Korea and southern Manchuria.[12][13][14][15][16][17][18][19]
